\begin_inset Formula $r\colon\left(2^{E}\times2^{E}\right)_{\subseteq}\to\mathbb{N}\cup\left\{ \infty\right\} $
\end_inset

 that maps a pair 
\begin_inset Formula $A\supseteq B$
\end_inset

